1. *Uzbudjena* sam zbog izleta u planine. (I'm excited about the mountain trip.)
2. Sinoć sam bila *uzbuđena* zbog važnog sastanka na poslu. (Last night I was excited about an important meeting at work.)
3. Kada sam videla da sam dobila nagradu, postala sam *uzbuđena*. (When I saw that I had won an award, I became excited.)
4. *Uzbudjena* sam što će mi doći prijatelji u goste. (I'm excited that my friends are coming to visit me.)
5. Ona je bila *uzbuđena* zbog svog prvog leta avionom. (She was excited about her first airplane flight.)
6. Zbog velikog broja posla, ona je bila *uzbuđena* i nervozna. (Because of the large amount of work, she was excited and nervous.)
7. Osetila je da joj srce brže kuca kada je videla svog idola i postala je jako *uzbuđena*. (She felt her heart beat faster when she saw her idol and became very excited.)
8. *Uzbudjena* sam da vidim ko će pobediti u takmičenju. (I'm excited to see who will win the competition.)
9. Kada je videla poklon koji joj je prijatelj kupio, postala je jako *uzbuđena*. (When she saw the gift her friend had bought for her, she became very excited.)
10. Ona je *uzbuđeno* pričala o svom putovanju u inostranstvo. (She talked excitedly about her trip abroad.)